OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA settled
OL,6,Fand clear night to come with gusty
OL,7,Fwinds over the hills to start with but
OL,8,Feasing through the night. Staying
OL,9,Frelatively mild with some places
OL,10,Fstaying in double figures.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FA bright start to Friday but
OL,13,Fturning cloudier into the afternoon
OL,14,Fwith showery outbreaks of rain pushing
OL,15,Fnorthwards. Showers becoming heavy,
OL,16,Fpossibly thundery by the evening. Warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
